# =============================================================================
#  Environment Configuration
#  =============================================================================
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#     copy .env.example .env
#
#  ⚠ SECURITY WARNINGS ⚠
#  1. The .env file IS listed in .gitignore — verify it stays there.
#  2. NEVER commit .env to version control. If you accidentally do,
#     rotate the key immediately at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#     and use git-filter-repo to purge it from history.
#  3. Never share your .env file via screenshots, pair-programming streams,
#     or pasting into issue trackers.
#  4. Use environment variables in CI/CD (GitHub Secrets, etc.) — never .env files.
#  5. Rotate keys every 90 days minimum. Monitor usage at:
#     https://platform.openai.com/usage
#  =============================================================================

# Your OpenAI API key (starts with "sk-proj-" for project keys)
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-your-actual-key-here"
